solution:
Through $O$ draw a line parallel to $\overline{AD}$ intersecting $\overline{PD}$ at $F$. [asy]
pair A,B,C,D,H,O,P,F;
O = (0,0);
P = (6,0);
H = (-6,0);
A = intersectionpoint(arc((A + H)/2, abs(A -  H)/2, 0, 180), arc(O, 2, 0, 180));
